data.description:
This property is available. Please inquire on this site to schedule a showing. 

This lowkey statement-architecture single-family home is AVAILABLE NOW

As the property is elevated, it undeniably features beautiful views of SF and Oakland perfect to enjoy with a cup of coffee or tea while looking at it from the patio/deck. Inside, the hardwood floors give life to the minimalist interior walls. The full kitchen boasts built-in wooden cabinetry great for storage and making it the accent of the area. Get ahold of a circular dining table because it will sit perfectly on its designated spot by the curved wall! The living room features large windows to get the view of the outside from the inside. This also allows a great amount of natural light inside the home that will give a bright and airy feel.

The location is as good as the aesthetics. You are near grocery stores, restaurants, and even parks with only less than 5-minutes drive!
Pets are allowed. Property with ADT Alarm System for extra security. Please read visit instructions when booking a showing.

Heating: ForcedAir
Cooling: None
Appliances: Washer, Dryer, Garbage Disposal, Range Oven, Refrigerator, Ceiling Fan, Patio, Balcony
Laundry: In Unit
Parking: Detached Garage, On Street, 1 spaces
Pets: Dogs Allowed, Cats Allowed

Security deposit: $3,230.00
Included Utilities: Garbage, Landscaping

Additional Deposit/Pet: $500.00

This property has a home security system.

Disclaimer: Ziprent is acting as the agent for the owner. Information Deemed Reliable but not Guaranteed. All information should be independently verified by renter.
